Introduction to this course :
=============================
In this 5-hours course, We will explore how Al can revolutionize Infrastructure as Code (lad) and cloud automation. Learn to automate cloud systems and optimize workflows with Al tools like Terraform, AWS, and GitHub Copilot
 
What I will be able to do after this course :
---------------------------------------------
Integrate Al in Infrastructure as Code for cloud automation
Master Vibe coding techniques for efficient lac development
Generate Terraform code and integrate it with AWS services
Use GitHub Copilot for Al-powered code generation
Optimize laC workflows with Al-driven agents
 
Course Instructor(s) :
---------------------
Gourav Shah is a DevOps expert with 15+ years of experience. He has taught over 65,000 students and delivered 300+ instructor-led workshops globally. He is the founder of Initcron and a published author on eDX.
 
Who is it for :
---------------
This course is perfect for software developers, DevOps engineers, and system architects with a basic understanding of cloud computing and programming. It's designed for those looking to enhance their skills in Al-driven infrastructure management and automation.

